 2023-05892023-06-16PCH
ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of KAREN HAMBERG of Delta, British Columbia, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Susan Jane Knott, whose term will expire, effective June 20, 2023.
